 <h4>Solution by Runge-Kutta RK4 method (explicit)</h4>
 <p>
  Differential equations (
  <a href="https://seamplex.com/feenox/examples/daes.html#the-double-pendulum">https://seamplex.com</a>
  )
 </p>
 <p>
  <span class="eq">
   <var>m</var>
   ·
   <var>l</var>
   <sub>1</sub>
   <sup>2</sup>
   ·
   <var>θ″</var>
   <sub>1</sub>
   +
   <var>m</var>
   <sub>2</sub>
   ·
   <var>l</var>
   <sub>1</sub>
   ·
   <var>l</var>
   <sub>2</sub>
   ·
